title: A Stroll Down Lovers Lane The Hall-Mills Mystery
description:
Hi Friends!
 Today on Murder, Mystery & Makeup, I wanted to talk about the Hall-Mills Mystery. It's an interesting story and sadly left unsolved. I think we all have an idea of who it could be but I would love to hear your thoughts and theories down below.
 Thank you so much for all your love and support, I love you guys. Hope to be seeing you very soon. Have a happy and safe rest of your day
xo
Bailey Sarian
